Hello,

Toodledo is a to-do service in the cloud

website." -- Good

* You may delete data from your account, or delete your entire account

* At its discretion, this site may remove any material posted on our web
site that infringes on the rights of others. --- Bad, it's we delete
first you can complain later.

Hopes this help,

Philippe
